Package com.mesosphere.sdk.testing

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CosmosRenderer
    Reads a service's Universe packaging configuration, and uses that to generate the resulting Scheduler environment.
    ServiceTestBuilder
    Exercises the service's packaging and Service Specification YAML file by building a Scheduler object against it.
    ServiceTestResult
    An object which contains the generated results from rendering a Service via ServiceTestBuilder.
    ServiceTestResult.TaskConfig
    An internal-only object for the result of generating a config file.
